request.html:
data [required]

object

Data for creating an enrollment.

attributes [required]

object

Attributes for creating an enrollment.

actions_allowlist [required]

[string]

List of allowed actions for the runner.

runner_host

string

The hostname for the runner. Required when push mode is enabled.

runner_modes [required]

[string]

The modes the runner should operate in.

runner_name [required]

string

The name of the on-prem runner.

type [required]

enum

The type of the resource. The value should always be enrollment. Allowed enum values: enrollment

200.html:
data [required]

object

Data for the enrollment status.

attributes [required]

object

Attributes for the enrollment status.

failure_reason [required]

string

The reason for enrollment failure, if applicable.

runner_id [required]

string

The runner identifier, if enrollment was successful.

status [required]

enum

The status of the enrollment. Allowed enum values: new,success,failed

id [required]

string

The token hash identifier.

type [required]

enum

The type of the resource. The value should always be getEnrollmentResponse. Allowed enum values: getEnrollmentResponse
